///   is `ADCn_CHm`.
/// - `$number`: the numbers extracted from `$signal`.
/// - `$gpio`: the name of the GPIO.
///
/// Example data:
/// - `(ADC2_CH5, GPIO12)`
/// - `((ADC2_CH5, ADCn_CHm, 2, 5), GPIO12)`
